        "created_at": "2021-03-22T16:57:28.255Z",
        "cooked": "<p>DR doesn\u2019t have any interaction with database clients, correct? That is, after a <code>switch</code> the clients connected to the old primary will just see the database being locked and the cluster file on all the clients doesn\u2019t get updated automatically to point to the new cluster.</p>",
